Package project

Class Motorcycle

java.lang.Object
project.Motorcycle
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Motorcycle extends Object implements Serializable
Instantiable class defining a Motorcycle object. This class contains methods allowing for the generation of an object via Vehicle Identification Numbers
See Also:
